                            subsidy award. Your comments will not be visible to the public.</label>
                        <textarea class="govuk-textarea" id="reject_reason_text" type="textarea"
                            name="reject_reason_text" rows="6"></textarea>


                        <div>
                            <button class="govuk-button govuk-button--warning" data-module="govuk-button">
